@CannibalusTrollamus I just beat her again today, and for a challenge decided to do it in as few turns as possible.... or rather, giving THEM as few turns as possible. Lady got one turn as I waited for Johnny so I could take the snaps, then it began.

I managed to take down the Umbral in one massive combo, took the malice dirge to the face, then killed her. So really, she only got one actual turn.

Granted, my lowest level character was Frank at 60, but it was still funny.
